{"tid":2304743,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇人揸中國車？","createTime":"2020-11-29T05:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T06:03:00.000Z","uid":157483,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"66a7e8bb1e55f1dd05de58dbb664fa65d6765186","tid":2304743,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"係外國識個台灣人<br />\n佢老豆係傳統賣台藍屍愛国撚黎 國民黨狂熱支持者果d<br />\n佢自己就正常既 藍綠都會撐下 視乎政治形勢<br />\n咁佢仲讀緊書 都未做野 <br />\n但佢考左車牌 自己又冇錢買車<br />\n咁佢老豆話將自己本身揸開架長城送比佢揸<br />\n自己又順便有藉口換部東風玩下<br />\n佢自己又冇咩所謂既 覺得有車揸好過冇 所以照揸<br />\n而且坐老豆呢部車都坐左5年 都叫有感情<br />\n佢話坐咁耐又冇話有咩大問題 <br />\n最近仲溝埋女（台灣妹） 成日車住條女出雙入對咁，條女又好似完全唔介意咁<br />\n<br />\n佢架車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqZ2JFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqZ2JFe.jpg&h=bdfc1260&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouUBN6W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouUBN6W.jpg&h=806bb936&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce07aa82c98398ab85f59299e6fb2a63c1655767","tid":2304743,"uid":34147,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"中國人揸中國車 啱"},{"pid":"94e537e1ff60883fd8e46a2174f1cac815318794","tid":2304743,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"ce07aa82c98398ab85f59299e6fb2a63c1655767","tid":2304743,"uid":34147,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"中國人揸中國車 啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"台灣人喎"},{"pid":"358bf28dc263be9fcbeff1cd4bdf48f2ccb4c341","tid":2304743,"uid":81353,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"車呢d 野, 好彩無事既由自可. <br />\n有起事上黎, 佢就同條女一鑊熟架啦"},{"pid":"ad6ba91d4c383526e9f5ba82b79e5e785caef16c","tid":2304743,"uid":157483,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"358bf28dc263be9fcbeff1cd4bdf48f2ccb4c341","tid":2304743,"uid":81353,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29